node.text:
This was so jokes…
 
To celebrate the launch of Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War, @CallofDuty challenged me to create an 80s inspired ‘look’ using archive @FilaUK items that feature in the new game.
 
The girls smashed it but I’m still fuming I didn’t snatch the prize 🤣 Check out @9p @taliamar @snoochieshy to see their look and decide who’s you think is best.
 
#BlackOpsColdWar @CallofDuty @FILAUK

node.text:
Big news, again! Last month, I asked you guys to showcase your fashion related talents, from styling to designing. I wanted to see YOUR talent. And well, you definitely brought it. Thank you to everyone who submitted to #21ShowReels. After watching them all, probably about 10 times each, my five favourite picks are - @torlambert , @houseofhersey , @being_a.blessin , @official_venusashu , @davidmjwholzapfel 
 
There's more my g's! In partnership with @Instagram, these next generation of creators have been selected as part of Instagram’s first 21 Under 21 list, along with other creators from art, music, sport and makeup - all aged 21 and under. 

I’ll also be featured in will be featured in a one-off digital zine in partnership with @guapmag – head to the link in my bio now to check them out!! #Instagram21under21 It's been a ride. Thanks for joining!
